title: Luke Bryan Sets The Record Straight On If He Tipped $1000 at Waffle House + 3 Name Celeb Game + Amy’s Fun Fact Friday
itunes:title: Luke Bryan Sets The Record Straight On If He Tipped $1000 at Waffle House + 3 Name Celeb Game + Amy’s Fun Fact Friday
description:
We talk to Luke Bryan about his new series on IMDB TV (Amazon), new single and if he was or wasn’t the mysterious $1000 tipper at a Waffle House in North Carolina. Bobby gives everyone the description of a celebrity with 3 names and the show has to guess who it is.
